trans-unit.source: Provides access to the property values of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern" /> object using its <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.Current" /> or <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.Cached" /> accessors.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona acceso a los valores de propiedades de un objeto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern" /> mediante sus descriptores de acceso <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.Current" /> o <see cref="P:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.Cached" />.

trans-unit.source: The properties in this structure can also be retrieved by using <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A>, using the corresponding identifiers from <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern>.
trans-unit.target: También se pueden recuperar las propiedades de esta estructura mediante <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCurrentPropertyValue%2A> y <xref:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement.GetCachedPropertyValue%2A>, utilizando los identificadores correspondientes de <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern>.

trans-unit.source: For example, The <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.DockPatternInformation.DockPosition%2A> property is identified by the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.DockPositionProperty> field.
trans-unit.target: Por ejemplo, el <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.DockPatternInformation.DockPosition%2A> propiedad se identifica mediante el <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern.DockPositionProperty> campo.

trans-unit.source: More information about the individual properties is available on the reference pages for those identifiers; see the link in the Remarks section of each reference topic.
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información acerca de las propiedades individuales está disponible en las páginas de referencia para esos identificadores; consulte el vínculo en la sección Comentarios de cada tema de referencia.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition" /> of an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement" /> within a docking container.
trans-unit.target: Recupera la enumeración <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition" /> de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.AutomationElement" /> dentro de un contenedor de acoplamiento.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition" /> of the element, relative to the boundaries of the docking container and other elements within the container.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition" /> del elemento, respecto a los límites del contenedor de acoplamiento y otros elementos del contenedor.

trans-unit.source: A docking container is a control that allows the arrangement of child elements, both horizontally and vertically, relative to the boundaries of the docking container and other elements within the container.
trans-unit.target: Un contenedor de acoplamiento es un control que permite la disposición de los secundarios elementos, tanto horizontal como verticalmente, con respecto a los límites del contenedor de acoplamiento y otros elementos dentro del contenedor.

trans-unit.source: In the following example, a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition> value is obtained representing the current dock position for a control that supports <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern>.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo siguiente, un <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPosition> se obtiene valor que representa la posición de acoplamiento actual para un control que admite <xref:System.Windows.Automation.DockPattern>.
